    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is looking for a new home and a little bit of elbow grease to get back to its best. While it currently requires some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity for someone who loves a good restoration project. If you're looking for a car with potential and are ready to put in the work, this is the one for you!",
