      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This unit remains in pristine, showroom condition, offering an unparalleled driving experience for the most discerning client. Meticulously inspected and free of any cosmetic or mechanical imperfections, it represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of such distinguished caliber.",
      "price": 46500.0,
